comment: Dedmon (ORL) sets the screen on Bradley (BOS) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Pressey (BOS) makes contact with Payton's (ORL) arm and causes him to lose the ball.
Pressey (BOS) maintains legal guarding position and makes contact with the ball while defending Payton's (ORL) drive.
Vucevic (ORL) sets the screen on Bradley (BOS) without giving him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Bass (BOS) cleanly blocks the layup attempt by Oladipo (ORL).
Harkless (ORL) makes contact with Bass' (BOS) arm as he dunks the ball.
Oladipo (ORL) and Harkless (ORL) trap Turner (BOS) and force the turnover.
Turner (BOS) cleanly strips the ball from Payton (ORL) on the play to the basket.
Crowder (BOS) makes contact with Payton's (ORL) arm on the play to the basket.
Gordon (ORL) wraps up Turner (BOS) following the inbound pass.
Vucevic (ORL) holds Bradley (BOS) while setting the screen and prevents him from contesting the jump shot.
Harris (ORL) commits a take foul on Smart (BOS).
